item.title: [Delta]AncientTeleports HELP!
item.dc:creator: @Continue Continue
item.description:
@Continue wrote:

You didn’t set it as a teleportation use. Try searching in your source files for lumbridge or varrock. If it comes up like this:

if (s == "Varrock") { teleX = 3210; teleY = 3424; addSkillXP((20*playerLevel[6]), 6); newheightLevel = 0; }

The s in if(s == “Varrock”) is the String. If you have something like that, change the teleX and teleY so that it teleports you somewhere. If you do not have it, try creating one, it’s not hard.

Read full topic
